# Project Structure Guide

This Next.js project follows a modern app directory structure:

- Main entry point is [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) which defines the root layout
- Core components are in [src/components](mdc:src/components)
- Utility functions are in [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts)
- Static assets are stored in the `public` directory
- Configuration files:
  - [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js) for Next.js configuration
  - [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) for Tailwind CSS
  - [.eslintrc.json](mdc:.eslintrc.json) for ESLint rules
